<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Doit1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Doit,</orth> the smallest piece of money, a trifle: <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.2.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 2, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 1.3.141" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 3, 141</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.112" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 112</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.4.60" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 4, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.217" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 217</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 4.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 2, 55</bibl>. <emph>irons of a d.</emph> (== worth a d.) <bibl n="shak. cor 1.5.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 5, 7</bibl>. <cit><quote>a dissension of a d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 4.4.17" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 17</bibl></cit>. In <bibl n="shak. ant 4.12.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 12, 37</bibl> O. Edd. <emph>dolts,</emph> M. Edd. blunderingly <emph>doits.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>